    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Kenmore?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kenmore property values are driven by block size, the Kenmore State High School catchment, the established leafy streetscape, and proximity to Indooroopilly without the Indooroopilly premium. Larger blocks on quiet residential streets away from Moggill Road consistently attract family buyers who want genuine land content and a settled suburban feel within practical commuting distance of the city.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Kenmore?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Kenmore homes typically sell within 30 to 45 days. The suburb draws buyers from a wide western corridor catchment, particularly families prioritising school catchments and block size, as well as interstate buyers who have identified the western suburbs as a value proposition relative to their origin cities.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Kenmore?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kenmore offers a quiet, family-oriented western suburbs lifestyle with generous blocks, leafy established streets and access to Mt Coot-tha bushland. Kenmore Village Shopping Centre provides practical everyday retail, and bus routes along Kenmore Road and Moggill Road connect to the CBD and Indooroopilly. The strong owner-occupier base gives the suburb a stable community character.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Kenmore a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kenmore sits at a compelling position in the western corridor, offering school catchments, block sizes and leafy character at a price point below Indooroopilly. Buyers who are priced out of Indooroopilly consistently find that Kenmore delivers comparable lifestyle fundamentals. The suburb's strong owner-occupier base and family demographic support consistent long-term demand.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

